{"type":"article","id":2810,"title":"你知道吗？曾经的长者网也有一个言论自由的匿名版。","uid":6760,"topics":[523,1406,2635,2913],"contents":"大前天考古长者网来着，竟然意外发现长者网有个匿名版。这里只提长者网的匿名版，剩下的部分我找时间另开一个帖子说一说。（2020.08.02更新，其余的部分已经在<a href=\"https://mohu.rocks/question/item_id-50036\">这个回答</a>里讲了。到时候我会开一个<a href=\"https://mohu.rocks/article/2948\">考古成果集合帖</a>。）<br>\n<br>\n为什么要单独把长者网考古的匿名版的部分放出来呢？很简单，就是因为前天品葱匿名版（葱2）爆炸的事情。我觉得葱2需要一个榜样。<br>\n<br>\n膜乎有一个帖子中包含了几张图片：<br>\n<a href=\"https://mohu.rocks/question/1303\">https://mohu.rocks/question/1303</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/RNZCwAl.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RNZCwAl.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/RNZCwAl.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/9uiUl1i.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9uiUl1i.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/9uiUl1i.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/IwtENS8.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IwtENS8.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/IwtENS8.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n长者网匿名版的链接为:<a href=\"https://h.zhangzhe.wang/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://h.zhangzhe.wang/</a><br>\n<br>\n若你想自行考古此匿名版，请点击这个链接：<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/*/https://h.zhangzhe.wang*\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/*/https://h.zhangzhe.wang*</a><br>\n<br>\n首先，进入匿名版时会有一个警告<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150222013158/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150222013158/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/HEuuCeD.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HEuuCeD.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/HEuuCeD.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n仅存的4个匿名版主页快照（时间可以在链接中看到）：<br>\n2015年2月23日<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150223122224/https://h.zhangzhe.wang/pixmicat.php?page_num=0\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150223122224/https://h.zhangzhe.wang/pixmicat.php?page_num=0</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/kw3dtM4.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kw3dtM4.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/kw3dtM4.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ENAnGXO.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ENAnGXO.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ENAnGXO.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/6EHdpXQ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6EHdpXQ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/6EHdpXQ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/dTloHrK.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dTloHrK.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/dTloHrK.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/kujxXIi.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kujxXIi.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/kujxXIi.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/pT3IhG9.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pT3IhG9.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/pT3IhG9.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wsgTtsg.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wsgTtsg.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/wsgTtsg.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/8p5AvwL.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8p5AvwL.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/8p5AvwL.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/6aVU9e0.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6aVU9e0.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/6aVU9e0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/inC5Zqg.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/inC5Zqg.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/inC5Zqg.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/B35VPyg.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/B35VPyg.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/B35VPyg.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/qlCCwkS.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qlCCwkS.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qlCCwkS.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/q18TP9E.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q18TP9E.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/q18TP9E.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n2015年2月23日<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150223162423/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/index.htm\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150223162423/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/index.htm</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/J1iUI1d.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/J1iUI1d.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/J1iUI1d.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/5gUEDhe.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5gUEDhe.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/5gUEDhe.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/qHMVXZo.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qHMVXZo.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qHMVXZo.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Hu0wZW6.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Hu0wZW6.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Hu0wZW6.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/rJnjz46.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rJnjz46.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/rJnjz46.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/kmdzt3g.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kmdzt3g.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/kmdzt3g.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/xNV5o53.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xNV5o53.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/xNV5o53.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/WI108a0.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WI108a0.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/WI108a0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZCtvWld.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZCtvWld.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZCtvWld.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/6wMGksi.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6wMGksi.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/6wMGksi.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n（剩下两个就不放图了，氛围也跟这两张差不多）<br>\n2015年2月24日<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150224164948/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?page_num=0\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150224164948/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?page_num=0</a><br>\n2015年4月7日<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150407003835/https://h.zhangzhe.wang/pixmicat.php?page_num=0\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150407003835/https://h.zhangzhe.wang/pixmicat.php?page_num=0</a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n然后就是匿名版的单条讨论，众多快照中只有这些存活：（res=多少就表明它是第多少条）<br>\n<br>\n第2条<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150223232935/http://h.zhangzhe.wang/pixmicat.php?res=2\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150223232935/http://h.zhangzhe.wang/pixmicat.php?res=2</a><br>\n<blockquote>匿名版已经建好了，测试了很多遍，也修复了不少BUG，弄了好几天，如果发现有什么问题可以加群280014358或者直接在这个串下面回复。<br>\n玩的开心(=ﾟωﾟ)=</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>吼啊</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>吼啊</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>吼啊 兹磁</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>还要学习一个</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>吼 滋词！</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>資磁</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>搞个大新闻</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>(＾o＾)ﾉ我滋糍</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>字体有点虚，还有点小( ´_ゝ`)</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>吼啊 滋词</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>真的要搞个大新闻了(´ﾟДﾟ`)</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>滋磁哇(＾o＾)ﾉ</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>经常有连接限制</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>把字体加大了一号，IE的反人类渲染我照顾不到|-` )<br>\n然后修复了引用功能，因为有一段代码我忘记改成服务器的参数了，现在可以用了(＾o＾)ﾉ<br>\n最后是滚动条，我决定不改</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>兹磁兹磁 make a big news！(＾o＾)ﾉ</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>&gt;&gt;No.46<br>\n已经修复了，现在应该没有连接限制了吧</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>求移动版，手机看着压力好大</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>&gt;&gt;No.74<br>\n嗯，之后我会兼容手机的，目前用户还不多，暂时先把目前的问题解决了( ´ー`)</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>匿名也要按照基本法</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>群被设置为不允许任何人加入了；w；(&gt;д&lt;)</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n第39条<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150224011948/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=39\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150224011948/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=39</a><br>\n<blockquote>無本文</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>&gt;&gt;No.39</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>左边大图长者对图样的记者怒不可遏右上图长者不屑一顾右下图长者语重心长</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>hhhhhhhh</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n第59条<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150224024936/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=59\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150224024936/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=59</a><br>\n<blockquote>不要一天想要搞个大新闻(´ﾟДﾟ`)</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>你搞得这个支援兵啊 伊克塞梯德</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n第118条<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150223232857/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=118\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150223232857/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=118</a><br>\n<blockquote><b>这里就是个专搞蛤蟆的地方？</b>难以理解</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>你啊，我感觉你还要学习一个。</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>毕竟还是还是too young！</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>too young啊| ω・´)</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>图样啊</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>奶已无 (;´Д`)你啊，毕竟还是图样，桑弹慕斯奶已无</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>啥叫蛤蟆应该叫牛蛙长者</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n第130条<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150224024757/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=130\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150224024757/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=130</a><br>\n<blockquote>升级了一下主机配置，宽带和并发数都有很大的提高，现在应该不会再出500错误了(ノﾟ∀ﾟ)ノ</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>正在写手机版的样式，希望这几天能够把手机版弄出来( ´ー`)</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n第135条<br>\nhttps://web.archive.org/web/20150224024802/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=135<br>\n<blockquote>作死教科书！</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>(　д ) ﾟ ﾟ</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>真是作死啊</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n第144条<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150223232901/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=144\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150223232901/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=144</a><br>\n<blockquote>好乖 乖乖</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>这谁？我说这妹子</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>&gt;&gt;No.149<br>\n不告诉你。</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>&gt;&gt;No.149<br>\n不告诉你。</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>&gt;&gt;No.149<br>\n那这老爷子的是谁？</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>月月鸟？</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>那女的是谁？</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>&gt;&gt;No.178<br>\n那不像月月鸟啊。感觉有点像一个演员，我国产剧看的太少，说不出是谁。</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n第148条<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150224024807/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=148\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150224024807/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=148</a><br>\n<blockquote>長者和禁評狂魔高下立判</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>像我姨夫..........</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>阳光，帅气(=ﾟωﾟ)=</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n第158条<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150224011900/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=158\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150224011900/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=158</a><br>\n<blockquote>续命后</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>这图配的妙</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>长者的这个吐舌技术太出色我怎么也学不会</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>&gt;&gt;No.199<br>\n我试了一下，真的学不会(つд⊂)</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n第166条<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150224024812/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=166\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150224024812/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=166</a><br>\n<blockquote>大家饿了吗？</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>I AM ANGRY!</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>你们啊，就想着搞个大新闻</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n第174条<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150224011905/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=174\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150224011905/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=174</a><br>\n<blockquote>度娘也要膜蛤</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>我觉得你们偶像界啊，还是要学习一个——</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>我今天作为一个偶像，有必要告诉你们一点，长者长者长(ゝ∀･)</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>蛤可蛤可蛤(*ﾟ∀ﾟ*)</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>我很抱歉，我今天是作为一个偶像宅跟你们讲。我不是爱抖露，但是我见得太多了。我有这个必要好告诉你们一点应援的经验。 我告诉你们，我是身经百战了，见得多啦！霓虹的哪一个爱抖露我没饭过？你们要知道，千代田的周刊文春，那比你们不知要高到哪里去了，我跟他谈笑风生。所以说新规呀还是要提高自己的知识水平，瓦嘎达？</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>江泽妮可</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n第179条<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150224024817/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=179\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150224024817/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=179</a><br>\n<blockquote>比你们不知高到哪里去了</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>七月份的尾巴，那是蛤蟆座|ー` )<br>\n八月份的前奏，那是蛤蟆座( ﾟ∀ﾟ)</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>膜蛤的时候，如果是个意外</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n第182条<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150224024833/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=182\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150224024833/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=182</a><br>\n<blockquote>人人网与长者</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>嗯 姿势不错</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n第183条<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150224024908/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=183\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150224024908/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=183</a><br>\n<blockquote>手机版第一帖(｀･ω･)</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>已知bug<br>\n不能发图看图<br>\n部分用户不能发帖<br>\n正在修复中</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>&gt;&gt;No.185<br>\n已经修复图片问题，如果还有不能发帖的用户，在电脑上发帖告诉我(*´д`)</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n第184条<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150223232906/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=184\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150223232906/http://h.zhangzhe.wang:80/pixmicat.php?res=184</a><br>\n<blockquote>强烈要求重开续命功能<br>\n我说要继续续命，你们滋瓷不滋瓷啊？</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>当然是兹磁啊( ﾟ∀。)</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>当然资辞啦</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>吼啊 资磁(｀･ω･)</blockquote><br>\n<blockquote>当然要资词啦</blockquote><br>